    {
      "id": "l8-clock",
      "type": "theory",
      "title": "Telling the time",
      "body": "# The clock\n\nFor clock time you need:\n\n| English | Hindi |\n|---|---|\n| Hour | घंटा |\n| Minute | मिनट |\n| Morning | सुबह |\n| Night | रात |\n\nTo ask the time, say **What time is it?** (क्या समय हुआ है?). To answer, English uses **It is ...**: *It is three o'clock* (तीन बजे हैं). The word **o'clock** is used only for a full hour."
    },
